  <br><button type="button" class="recipe-item">Mix together all ingredients until well combined.</button>
  <br><button type="button" class="recipe-item">Line a cookie sheet with parchment paper, or use a baking stone.</button>
  <br><button type="button" class="recipe-item">Using a small cookie scoop, drop dough onto the the cookie sheet, and then flatten into round shapes.</button>
  <br><button type="button" class="recipe-item">Bake approx. 20 â€“ 25 minutes, or until golden.</button>
